observer (1.0.9) testing; urgency=medium

  * Switch between the remind and history dialogs without nesting modals: F12
    from the remind dialog closes it and opens history; F12 or Esc in history
    closes history and reopens the remind dialog with saved input.
  * Rename ObservationDialog to RemindDialog and StatisticsDialog to
    HistoryFrame.
  * Run DeepSeek in the main process; replace wxWebView with a native WebKit pane
    and persistent site data.
  * Add DeepSeek history-search RPA to reuse an existing chat before submitting
    a new prompt.
  * Hand off to history or quote AI from the remind dialog without losing
    draft scores and activity text.

