observer (1.0.5) testing; urgency=medium

  * Ignore history statistics samples whose energy, mood, and grounding are all
    still at the default score.
  * Rename --sqlite-db to --database and raise the default --cancel to 5.
  * Remap prompt shortcuts: F8 snoozes, F1 opens history, F2-F4 decrease
    grounding/mood/energy, and remove Ctrl+H.
  * Update README and man pages for the CLI and shortcut changes.
  * Remove Win+Alt+G and Win+Alt+H X11 global hotkeys; wake through desktop
    launcher shortcuts and single-instance IPC instead.
  * Open statistics/history when oremind is launched twice in quick succession
    while waiting.
  * Remap prompt shortcuts: F1 opens history; F2-F4 decrease
    grounding/mood/energy; F5-F7 increase energy/mood/grounding.
  * Add Simplified Chinese man page and update English man page and README.
  * Drop the direct libx11 build dependency.
  * Fix GTK tray icon black borders by trimming icon backdrop padding and
    adding a 32-bit alpha channel before creating wxIcon.
  * Switch bundled app icons to icon-256.png and drop icon-light.png and
    icon-dark.png.

